data.description:
Welcome to this gorgeous home in the desirable gated community of Stone Butte. This luxurious home has a well-thought-out floor plan featuring 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, an open den, and a resort-style backyard! The chef's kitchen is gorgeous with modern staggered cabinetry, Quartz countertops, beautiful tile backsplash, stainless steel wall appliances, and a sleek gas cooktop and range. The wood-like tile, neutral wall tones, and 9 ft ceilings create a bright and clean aesthetic, perfect for any style. The primary suite is spacious with recessed canned lighting, a walk-in closet, and a spa-like ensuite bathroom featuring a dual sink vanity and a tiled shower. The remaining bedrooms are move-in ready and spotless and complete with blinds. The backyard is an entertainer's dream! The covered patio extends out to a deck and a refreshing pool with a serene water feature. Bask in the AZ sunsets from this dream backyard! Additional features include a water softener, security cameras, a garage service door, and a 2' garage extension. Do not miss out on this home!

 

Nestled in a prime North Phoenix location, Stone Butte is a gated community with plenty to offer! Situated near a major freeway and near the JW Marriott Desert Ridge, golf courses, shopping centers, mountain trails, and fine dining establishments, residents enjoy a lifestyle that seamlessly integrates leisure, accessibility, and a rich array of amenities.
